    <title>Self-Cure Net 阅读笔记</title>
    <url>/2021/03/07/article-title/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/acceptedday/article/details/104884235">参考自https://blog.csdn.net/acceptedday/article/details/104884235</a><br><a href="https://github.com/kaiwang960112/Self-Cure-Network">https://github.com/kaiwang960112/Self-Cure-Network</a></p>
<hr>
<p>[TOC]</p>
<h1 id="Self-Cure-Net-阅读笔记"><a href="#Self-Cure-Net-阅读笔记" class="headerlink" title="Self-Cure Net 阅读笔记"></a>Self-Cure Net 阅读笔记</h1><h2 id="简单摘要"><a href="#简单摘要" class="headerlink" title="简单摘要"></a>简单摘要</h2><p>  该网络（简称SCN）可以在面部表情识别中，抑制不确定性并防止深度网络过度拟合不确定的面部图像。<br>  主要有两个方面：<br>      （1）采用自注意力，对排名规则化以对训练样本加权<br>      （2）对低排名样本重标记</p>
<h2 id="主要模块："><a href="#主要模块：" class="headerlink" title="主要模块："></a>主要模块：</h2><h3 id="（1）自注意力重要性加权-Self-Attention-Importance-Weighting"><a href="#（1）自注意力重要性加权-Self-Attention-Importance-Weighting" class="headerlink" title="（1）自注意力重要性加权(Self-Attention Importance Weighting)"></a>（1）自注意力重要性加权(Self-Attention Importance Weighting)</h3><blockquote>
<p>通过CNN网络提取到一系列特征后（如F = [x1,x2,…,xn])将该FC层通过 $\alpha_i = \sigma(W_a^Tx_i)$ 得到一系列权重。在原文提供的源码中，使用resnet18作为backbone network。</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">def __init__(self, pretrained &#x3D; True, num_classes &#x3D; 7, drop_rate &#x3D; 0):</span><br><span class="line">    super(Res18Feature, self).__init__()</span><br><span class="line">    self.drop_rate &#x3D; drop_rate</span><br><span class="line">    resnet  &#x3D; models.resnet18(pretrained)</span><br><span class="line">    # self.feature &#x3D; nn.Sequential(*list(resnet.children())[:-2]) # before avgpool</span><br><span class="line">    self.features &#x3D; nn.Sequential(*list(resnet.children())[:-1]) # after avgpool 512x1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    fc_in_dim &#x3D; list(resnet.children())[-1].in_features # original fc layer&#39;s in dimention 512</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line">    self.fc &#x3D; nn.Linear(fc_in_dim, num_classes) # new fc layer 512x7</span><br><span class="line">    self.alpha &#x3D; nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(fc_in_dim, 1),nn.Sigmoid())</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">def forward(self, x):</span><br><span class="line">    x &#x3D; self.features(x)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    if self.drop_rate &gt; 0:</span><br><span class="line">        x &#x3D;  nn.Dropout(self.drop_rate)(x)</span><br><span class="line">    x &#x3D; x.view(x.size(0), -1)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    attention_weights &#x3D; self.alpha(x)</span><br><span class="line">    out &#x3D; attention_weights * self.fc(x)</span><br><span class="line">    return attention_weights, out</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>原文中损失函数采用对数加权交叉熵损失（WCE-Loss）：<br>$\mathcal{L}<em>{WCE} = - {1\over N} \sum</em>{i=1}^N \log{\frac{e^{\alpha_iW_{yi}^Tx_i}}{\sum_{j=1}^Ce^{\alpha_iW_{j}^Tx_i}}}$</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="（2）排序正则化（RankRegularization）"><a href="#（2）排序正则化（RankRegularization）" class="headerlink" title="（2）排序正则化（RankRegularization）"></a>（2）排序正则化（RankRegularization）</h3><blockquote>
<p>通过（1）得到样本权重$\alpha_i$($\alpha\in(0,1)$),然后对权重降序排列(权重高则说明样本有较高“重要性”)，分为比率为$\beta$的两组（高重要组：$M=\beta N$,低重要组：N-M），再分别取平均值$\alpha_H$和$\alpha_L$。<br>$$\alpha_H={\frac{1}{M}}\sum_{i=0}^M\alpha_i,\alpha_L={\frac{1}{N-M}}\sum_{M}^N\alpha_i$$<br>同时定义排序正则化损失（RR-Loss）：<br>$$\mathcal{L}<em>{RR} = max{0,\delta_1 - (\alpha_H-\alpha_L)}$$<br>其中$\delta_1$是一个超参数。将（1）与（2）中两损失函数以一定比率相加遍得总损失函数：$\mathcal{L}<em>all=(1-\gamma)\mathcal{L}</em>{RR}+\gamma\mathcal{L}</em>{WCE}$。</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Rank Regularization</span><br><span class="line">        _, top_idx &#x3D; torch.topk(attention_weights.squeeze(), tops)</span><br><span class="line">        _, down_idx &#x3D; torch.topk(attention_weights.squeeze(), batch_sz - tops, largest &#x3D; False)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        high_group &#x3D; attention_weights[top_idx]</span><br><span class="line">        low_group &#x3D; attention_weights[down_idx]</span><br><span class="line">        high_mean &#x3D; torch.mean(high_group)</span><br><span class="line">        low_mean &#x3D; torch.mean(low_group)</span><br><span class="line">        # diff  &#x3D; margin_1 - (high_mean - low_mean)</span><br><span class="line">        diff  &#x3D; low_mean - high_mean + margin_1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        if diff &gt; 0:</span><br><span class="line">            RR_loss &#x3D; diff</span><br><span class="line">        else:</span><br><span class="line">            RR_loss &#x3D; 0.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="（3）重标记（Relabeling）："><a href="#（3）重标记（Relabeling）：" class="headerlink" title="（3）重标记（Relabeling）："></a>（3）重标记（Relabeling）：</h3><blockquote>
<p>不确定的样本有较低重要性，因此对低重要性组进行重标签：<br>$$<br>y’ =<br>\begin{cases}<br>    l_{max},\ \   if \ P_{max}-P_{gt}&gt;\delta_2 \<br>    l_{org},\ \   otherwise<br>\end{cases}<br>$$<br>若有最大预测的概率与给定标签概率之差大于阈值delta_2，则更换标签为该索引，否则保存原标签。重标签完成后遍可丢回训练集。</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Relabel samples</span><br><span class="line">if i &gt;&#x3D; args.relabel_epoch:</span><br><span class="line">    sm &#x3D; torch.softmax(outputs, dim &#x3D; 1)</span><br><span class="line">    Pmax, predicted_labels &#x3D; torch.max(sm, 1) # predictions</span><br><span class="line">    Pgt &#x3D; torch.gather(sm, 1, targets.view(-1,1)).squeeze() # retrieve predicted probabilities of targets</span><br><span class="line">    true_or_false &#x3D; Pmax - Pgt &gt; margin_2</span><br><span class="line">    update_idx &#x3D; true_or_false.nonzero().squeeze() # get samples&#39; index in this mini-batch where (Pmax - Pgt &gt; margin_2)</span><br><span class="line">    label_idx &#x3D; indexes[update_idx] # get samples&#39; index in train_loader</span><br><span class="line">    relabels &#x3D; predicted_labels[update_idx] # predictions where (Pmax - Pgt &gt; margin_2)</span><br><span class="line">    train_loader.dataset.label[label_idx.cpu().numpy()] &#x3D; relabels.cpu().numpy() # relabel samples in train_loader</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="小结"><a href="#小结" class="headerlink" title="小结"></a>小结</h2><blockquote>
<p>SCN通过自注意力及排名正则化机制对“模糊”的样本进行重标签，从而降低了样本不确定性对训练深度神经网络的影响。同时，SCN的端到端训练特点，使其易于与各种CNN网络结合。</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
